            <h2>Beliefs</h2>
            <p>Christians believe in the Holy Trinity, consisting of God the Father, God the Son (Jesus Christ), and God the Holy Spirit. They also believe in the divinity of Jesus Christ, his death, and resurrection, and that faith in him leads to salvation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Bible</h2>
            <p>The Bible is the holy scripture of Christianity, divided into the Old Testament and the New Testament. It contains religious texts, history, poetry, and teachings relevant to Christian faith and practice.</p>
        </div>
